{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>57歲視帝「馬神」馬德鐘，1993年因拍攝廣告被發掘入行後，曾是無綫千禧年代的當家小生之一。他在2011年一度離巢北上發展，近年以部頭合約形式回歸，憑《跳躍生命線》勇奪視帝寶座。他今年初再度宣布離開TVB，馬德鐘否認息影，又指與TVB關係良好，並非不歡而散。馬德鐘日前現身內地開騷，拜神燒香求北上發展順利，兼Deep V吸客，相當賣力！</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20250126/960304334455836672569087.jpeg/xlOm3l0lXZbBikoET2O-Ig7RCVZRAXKtJOP3ZSTj92U\" alt=\"馬德鐘當年憑《跳躍生命線》奪得視帝殊榮。（TVB）\"><figcaption>馬德鐘當年憑《跳躍生命線》奪得視帝殊榮。（TVB）</figcaption></figure><p>馬德鐘燒香拜神求北上順利</p><p>馬德鐘離開TVB後機會不斷，再度轉戰內地，與各TVB藝人一樣開拓音樂市場。而馬德鐘在內地人氣不俗，馬德鐘與陳煒一齊出席活動，燒香又拜神，祈求一切順利，相當神心。</p><p>馬德鐘之後開騷，他穿上Deep V騷出好身材，多年來外表狀態保持得極佳；馬德鐘又唱又跳，57歲有氣有力，體能十分不錯。他又到台下與觀眾握手互動，相當親民。台下觀眾亦熱情萬分，上前摸馬神手仔，看來馬德鐘在內地人氣不錯！</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123049482951856128153928.png/UxpynToyHrtZUG2t_lIfra0zhNEEHbTCS-sqv0vrKr8\" alt=\"馬德鐘燒香拜神。（小紅書）\"><figcaption>馬德鐘燒香拜神。（小紅書）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123049479873105920412065.png/o02rXszuw4SoDivO0hJ-810Z7uQo_v_rUk6nPlJOpz4\" alt=\"馬德鐘與陳煒。（小紅書）\"><figcaption>馬德鐘與陳煒。（小紅書）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123049477205397504639041.png/YP_drqD-JhbQqXBTAB2wfrZZ3UlhmjKyjgBHCI4ARwg\" alt=\"Deep V開騷。（小紅書）\"><figcaption>Deep V開騷。（小紅書）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123049474491551744145039.png/hT3HlesQyuBvPzFs9JfdGGAX1owc3yfUq3O3wKtzt8A\" alt=\"台下觀眾熱情。（小紅書）\"><figcaption>台下觀眾熱情。（小紅書）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123049471425384448975038.png/ZzoWyxSpM2-n6nHI-m8FvDNIrlINZQdr05kkudOZJLk\" alt=\"馬神好受歡迎。（小紅書）\"><figcaption>馬神好受歡迎。（小紅書）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123049489780183040481725.png/qxYCycyb3x_T5CM0E9sGwXhsizbkgB9IM53KrDOdyqw\" alt=\"馬德鐘分享多張靚相。（小紅書）\"><figcaption>馬德鐘分享多張靚相。（小紅書）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123049487208943616013976.png/syvPjAz9hsAGn1F5HKUQA-h6sSlBt6i3bWftyW1n7ck\" alt=\"靚仔！（小紅書）\"><figcaption>靚仔！（小紅書）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123049484344102912594167.png/PVcSvdps4Ki2qE8E_0GF3hroN3R_LvuM63HRFetx0RU\" alt=\"又與陳煒。（小紅書）\"><figcaption>又與陳煒。（小紅書）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123049481466679296156297.png/WBfSrkJXbjde6xcSWREORAj8l6loxW4U5VdvSOVXb0g\" alt=\"勁！（小紅書）\"><figcaption>勁！（小紅書）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260421/1123049478350180352214078.png/6BmFoiFQW9jso2uWS-R7s8jSaY-sbZFxgLycgYC8nIE\" alt=\"內地有人氣！（小紅書）\"><figcaption>內地有人氣！（小紅書）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-22T00:52:54.873021+00:00","quality":{"score":2,"chars":521,"images":11,"source":"HK01 娛樂","fallback":"none"}}